quran[5]{c,v,t,f}:
  113,4,"“Ni ku yakusakala ya (asaŵi) ŵaakupepela mu iwundo (pakuloga).”"
  113,5,"“Ni ku yakusakala ya jwalitima ndema jajukutenda litima.”"
  114,1,"Jilani: “Ngulijuya mwa M'mbuje jwa ŵandu.”"
  114,2,"“Nchimwene jwa ŵandu.” ",1:[Pa kaŵechete ka Allah kanti: “Nchimwene jwa ŵandu.” Akusimulila Abȗ Hurairah رضى الله عنه yanti: Nampikene Ntenga jwa Allahﷺjuchitiji: “Allah tachiliwumbata litaka, ni kugaŵiliga mawunde ni nkono Wakwe wan’dyo, kaneka ni tachiti: ‘Une ni Nchimwene. Ali kwapi achaiŵenye ŵa pa chilambo?” (Swahîh Al-Bukhârî, Hadith No. 5434).]
  114,3,"“Nnungu jwa ŵandu.”"